      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 665: The no-recorder path creates a video file and assigns mCurrentPhoto before checking resolveActivity(). If no video capture activity is available, the method returns with an orphan temp file and stale mCurrentPhoto. Check activity availability before creating the output file, or delete/reset on failure.\n```suggestion\nval intent \u003d Intent(MediaStore.ACTION_VIDEO_CAPTURE)\nif (intent.resolveActivity(context.packageManager) \u003d\u003d null) {\n    Toast.makeText(activity, R.string.video_recorder_error, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show()\n    return\n}\nintent.apply {\n    putExtra(MediaStore.EXTRA_VIDEO_QUALITY, 0)\n    putExtra(MediaStore.EXTRA_OUTPUT, ContentUri.getUriForFile(context, AndroidFileUtils.createVideoFile(context).apply {\n        mCurrentPhoto \u003d this\n    }))\n}\n```",
